prompts.frontCover: A flat 2D watercolor painting of a charming, slightly disheveled cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, clinging upside-down to a vibrant, leafy tree branch. The sloth has a wide, sleepy, blissful smile on its face. Soft, flowing colors and artistic paint bleeds create a lighthearted and dreamy atmosphere on a textured paper background. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday! Let's get wild... or at least move to the other side of the couch."
